snippet.title: Bionic Bay - Six One Indie Showcase Trailer
snippet.description: A scientist uses a unique teleportation instrument to escape an ancient biomechanical world filled with imaginative technology, deadly traps, and hidden secrets. See some of the dangers you'll face in this new trailer for Bionic Bay, an upcoming action-adventure platforming game coming to PC in 2025. A demo for Bionic Bay is available now on Steam.
